<h1>Almonds</h1>
<p>
Almonds are one of the most commonly consumed dry fruits. They provide immense health benefits to people of all age groups. They can be consumed raw, soaked, or roasted.
Benefits:<br>

Treat heart diseases<br>
manage blood sugar level<br>
Help with weight management<br>
1 ounce (28g) serving of Almonds:<br>

Protein 6 grams<br>
Fiber 4 grams<br>
Plus Vitamin E (35% of Daily Value)<br>
Magnesium (20% of Daily Value)<br>
Calcium (8% of Daily Value)<br>
</p>
